<Layout
  title="Woori Acupuncture - Traditional Korean Medicine & Acupuncture in Riverside, CA"
  description="Professional acupuncture and traditional Korean herbal medicine services in Riverside, California. Treating menstrual cramps, acne, anxiety, pain management, arthritis, Parkinson's, menopause, infertility, digestive disorders, stroke recovery, diabetes, high blood pressure, weight management, skin issues, and insomnia."
  lang="en"
  canonical="https://wooriacu.com/"
  siteName="Woori Acupuncture"
  locale="en_US"
  hreflangEn="https://wooriacu.com/"
  hreflangEs="https://wooriacu.com/es/"
  keywords="acupuncture, Korean medicine, herbal medicine, pain relief, traditional medicine, Riverside CA, natural healing, wellness, holistic health, menstrual cramps, acne treatment, anxiety relief, arthritis treatment, Parkinson's disease, menopause, infertility, digestive disorders, stroke recovery, Bell's palsy, diabetes, high blood pressure, weight management, skin conditions, insomnia, Crohn's disease"
